    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Bleakwood</strong> 是一款颠覆国际象棋传统观念的肉鸽类牌组构建游戏。在这个邪恶的奇幻世界中，只有拥抱腐化才能走向权力巅峰。通过解锁卡牌、强化单位和牺牲棋子，一步一步变得更加强大，最终将对手踩在脚下。但是古语有云“恃德者昌，恃力者亡”。你是否会选择舍弃道德来夺回属于自己的权力？</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >扭曲的国际象棋</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021800/extras/2cda1b77951164fe3fdce9651c3403c1.poster.avif?t=1762278056\" width=616 height=347 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021800/extras/2cda1b77951164fe3fdce9651c3403c1.webm?t=1762278056\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款颠覆了传统规则的重制版国际象棋游戏。利用强大的卡牌来强化能力和控制单位，但强大的力量需要付出高昂的代价。每一次强化都会导致腐化传播，当腐化过度的时候，你的军团就会从内部分崩离析。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >致命的卡牌组合</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021800/extras/22da457e48665d2982e2df5a15207942.poster.avif?t=1762278056\" width=616 height=347 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021800/extras/22da457e48665d2982e2df5a15207942.webm?t=1762278056\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >卡牌是你的致胜武器，但也暗藏祸根。操纵能力、移动、角色和环境；巧妙地组合卡牌，产生毁灭性的效果，给敌人以致命打击。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >混乱的棋盘</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021800/extras/328d586c2b774dd1d1fb34c37222c1b1.poster.avif?t=1762278056\" width=616 height=347 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021800/extras/328d586c2b774dd1d1fb34c37222c1b1.webm?t=1762278056\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >棋盘上布满诡异的陷阱，环境中充斥着危险。穿越险恶重重的地形，征服混乱动荡的王国，或者在征途中命丧黄泉。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >腐化轮回</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021800/extras/ef7f1092e73dd0c69bcd789481658341.poster.avif?t=1762278056\" width=616 height=347 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021800/extras/ef7f1092e73dd0c69bcd789481658341.webm?t=1762278056\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你前进的每一步都将留下腐化的痕迹。构建威力强大的卡牌库，任由黑暗和不断强化的力量将你吞噬。定制你的卡牌组合，招募并强化你的军团，磨练你的玩法。棋盘终有重置时，而你已永堕腐化轮回。</p>",
